text: The Trinidad and Tobago national netball team represent Trinidad and Tobago in international netball competition and are governed by Trinidad and Tobago Netball Association. They have attended the Netball World Cup since 1963 except in 1991. Their best result joint 1st in 1979. Category:National sports teams of Trinidad and Tobago Category:Netball in the Americas
title: Trinidad and Tobago national netball team
